 psykiske lidelser.", "Hvis vi ikke gj\u00f8r det, m\u00e5 vi slutte \u00e5 lure p\u00e5 hvorfor folk mister tiltro til systemet, dropper ut av skolen og begynner \u00e5 stemme p\u00e5 politikere \u00e0 la Donald Trump."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "0a43949461e72f2af29d8b0b2989ea29b0c7ab9cac5aaeade5ba85be5a90bbc1"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-17T19:22:03.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Du har kanskje h\u00f8rt dem? Velmenende voksne samlet rundt et kaffebord, samtalende om s\u00e5kalt oppeg\u00e5ende ungdom."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article14737200.ece/y3njnt/ALTERNATES/w980-default/tb895acb.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/02d266986d25e0ad79a2a543b5ca0c26ffc26e25.jpg?591cb053"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Bill.merk. oppeg\u00e5ende ungdom -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "02d266986d25e0ad79a2a543b5ca0c26ffc26e25"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Ungdom", "Oppvekst", "Ten\u00e5ringer", "Marte Hallem"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Ungdom,Oppvekst,Ten\u00e5ringer,Marte Hallem"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "meninger"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["oppeg\u00e5ende ungdom", "ungdom", "oppeg\u00e5ende"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["saupstad og kolstad", "filippa k", "bill", "r\u00f8ff", "kygo", "cubus"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["donald trump", "kari l\u00f8vendal mogstad"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["pluss/meninger", "pluss"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/meninger/article14737200.ece/y3njnt/ALTERNATES/w980-default/tb895acb.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "va